&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;img src="/articles/0020/3816/tecseis.jpg1273167616" height="101" alt="Tecseis" style="border: 1px solid black; float: right; margin: 8px;" width="182"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
